69 Robinson Avenue is prominently located on the corner of Robinson Avenue and Campbell Street, within the established commercial precinct of Belmont approximately 8 kilometres south east of the Perth Central Business District. This location has excellent access to Great Eastern Highway, Tonkin Highway and public transport.

The building consists of an office and workshop with access off both Robinson Avenue and Campbell Street. The office area is carpeted and air-conditioned and benefits from partitioned offices. The workshop area has three phase power and three sliding door access points. There is parking to the front of the property and parking and hardstand to the rear.

The property also provide male and female amenities and a kitchen.

The workshop also includes a training room of approx. 100sqm which is air-conditioned.

LAND AREA                        2,110sqm

Office                                       252sqm
Workshop                               793sqm


For further information please contact Colm McHugh on 0420 312 645.

CBRE are the appointed exclusive selling and leasing Agents for this superb Belmont property.

Properties on major arterial roads within the Belmont commercial/industrial precinct do not come along very often.

This is an excellent opportunity to either occupy or invest in 157 - 159 Abernethy Road.

Building areas :

Office/amenities -              679 sqm

Warehouse/workshop -  1,315 sqm

Total land area -             4,350 sqm

This property represents a very attractive entry level to purchase or lease in a prime location for the up and coming Belmont area.

Asking rental : $240,000 pa net

Asking price : $3,200,000 ( Plus GST if applicable )

Warick Irving 0413 863 335

CBRE are pleased to present for sale this unique commercial development opportunity at 8 Robinson Avenue, Belmont.

The 3,979sqm* site possess a 133m* frontage to Robinson Avenue and is located within Belmonts established commercial precinct, nearby to major industrial precincts and Perth Airports. 

Situated 7.8km* east of the Perth CBD, the site provides good accessibility to major thoroughfares of the locality such as Great Eastern Highway, Orrong Road and Abernethy Road.

The contour of the site slopes downward away from Robinson Avenue, overlooking Severin Walk and creating the potential for elevated views back toward the Swan River.

Zoned mixed-business under the City of Belmonts LPS No. 15, the site is well suited to a broad range of end uses, having previously been DA approved for a 3-level office building. 

This exceptional development site is for sale via an Offers Invited campaign closing Thursday 15th October 2020 at 4pm.
